      "created_at": "2024-01-25T11:49:31.230Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex</p>\n<p>I am back now doing all of my workouts in slope mode on my fixed gear bike which is great. However there is just one small thing that I would like looked at.</p>\n<p>When creating the workouts I am not allowed to creat a slope interval at 0% The box is not blank and I have tried both 0 &amp; 0.0 without success. So instead I have to manually adjust the slope each time I do a 0% interval.</p>\n<p>So would it be possible for the workout creator/editor to be modified to allow 0% or 0.0% as the slope setting?</p>\n<p>Many thanks from a long term user who has seen so many improvements and enhancements to a fantastic cycling app.</p>\n<p>Kind regards</p>\n<p>Karl</p>",
